	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_72137"><p>
If the Counter / LazyIterator example was written in Perl 5, one would use '<code>sub { $count++ }</code>', isn't it?  Why the same method, i.e. '<code>sub { }</code>' as circumfix operator for block in Perl 6?

</p><p>
P.S. Would you resubmit this blog post to <a href="http://perlgeek.de/blog-en" title="perlgeek.de" rel="nofollow">http://perlgeek.de/blog-en</a> [perlgeek.de] for it to be easier to find?</p></div>
		
	
